title: Doctor Who Complete Season 02, 1964-1965, William Hartnell
description:
All 39 episodes of the 1964/65 season of Doctor Who, featuring the First Doctor and his companions: Susan Foreman, Barbara Wright, Vicki, and Steven Taylor.

Includes reconstructions using photographs taken on set and recovered segments of footage, along with the audio recordings of the episodes, to recreate missing episodes. Visual quality varies depending on the reconstruction.
